summary: Do you have headcanons for like - canon Moomin and Snufkin heights in relationship to non- moomin valley people? Like when...
question: Do you have headcanons for like - canon Moomin and Snufkin heights in relationship to non- moomin valley people? Like when Snufkin leaves for the winter- is he like a weird feral cat to other people? I have questions.
answer:
I definetely see him as below average, since i see Joxter as a tiny stinky man. For Moomintroll, he´s average for a Moomin but around the same height as Snufkin, so tinier than the average Mumrik

(Also Mymble’s daughter for reference, since i imagine The Mymble being even taller)
